changelist.comment: Implemented one new method in SimpleLinkedCircularList and DoubleLinkedCircularList. Method: retrnNodedata(int index) [returns tha data of a node by an index]

task.summary: Added SimpleList for implementation of game stages
Added directories and SimpleLinkedList is complete, part of [PD-06] user storie.
Implemented DoubleLinkedList and it's methods.
Implemented method for getting a node, given it´s position on list, and print and reversePrint in doubly linked list.
Added images for the help window, bug makes images dont appear on window.
Solved Bug that caused trouble with images on help window
Added the MainMenu screen to the game and fixed some bugs
Implemented class Phase for management of the intersections and joints of phases.
Moved the generatePhase method, to the Phase.generatePhases method, for simplifying code.
Fixed bugs on .len() methods on CircularDoubleList and DoubleLinkedList
Method Player.calcRoute can return a SimpleLinkedList with all the possible boxes to move, given an it, that is the result of rolling the dices. Bug when try to move from a Phase thats not the main.
Finished [PD-57] main table is generated with random boxes and intersections, done method for finding all possible boxes to go after rolling dices.
Updates on the class Player, singleton on the Table class. Added Game class.
Added all clases for the event stack, and implemented the earn 2-5 stars and lose one star events, on the Stars class.
Implemented the steal coins event, and the method Player.modifyCoins.
Created the input manager window, for finding the possible ways in the table, from the gui
Can choose where to move from the result of the DiceSimulator
Functional moving through the table. :)
Solved bug when moving through the end of a circular list.
ready the implementation of mechanism for controlling the facing of two players on the same box
Fixed bug that generated exception when moving one space on a phase, and ready one way moving on phase D.
